/--
The following square is a pullback

      PGrpd ------ toPCat ------> PCat
        |                           |
        |                           |
 PGrpd.forgetToGrpd          PCat.forgetToCat
        |                           |
        v                           v
      Grpd------forgetToCat------->Cat
